plptool.mips

Class SimCore.mem

  • java.lang.Object
    • plptool.mips.SimCore.mem
  • Enclosing class:
    SimCore

    public class SimCore.mem
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the memory (MEM) stage of the PLP CPU pipeline. Writeback module is attached to this class. The bus module is also attached to this class, and it is the only place where the PLP CPU simulation core interacts with the outside world aside from fetching instructions in IF stage.
